* Better visualization of NURBS surfaces
- Slicing, mean and gauss maps
- Density change for slicing
* Lighting problems of mesh files (reversed normals, lack of shadows)
* Other input file formats (e.g. STL, IGES)
* Other output file formats (e.g. PNG)
* Gauss/mean histograms
* Speedup
